title: Your Best, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO120
description: "I'm doing my best." That's what people say all the time. But Andy Frisella asks, "what is your best?"  According to The MFCEO, "your best" is always developing, always evolving. That's why you can't ever really say you've achieved your best. Instead, you should be constantly pushing yourself to your best, which will always be just out of your reach.
